    "14069655": {
      "title": "Inverse boundary value problem for Maxwell equations with local data",
      "abstract": "We prove a uniqueness theorem for an inverse boundary value problem for the Maxwell system with boundary data assumed known only in part of the bound- ary. We assume that the inaccessible part of the boundary is either part of a plane, or part of a sphere. This work generalizes the results obtained by Isakov for the Schr\\\"odinger equation to Maxwell equations."
